<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Albrecht von Wertheim, Bischof von Bamberg</head><p>Der Rat bestätigt dem Matthias Wenigheinz, Bürger zu Nürnberg, eheliche Abstammung und guten Leumund und kündigt Marquart Waltmann, Diener der Stadt, an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_11" id="4r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_11_r1l2">Bẏſſchoff cʒu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> / oder wer <expan>ſeıne<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l3">hat in geiſtlıchen ſachen</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_11_r1l4"><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> Als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden vormals <expan>geſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l5">vnd beẏ dem <expan>Markart<ex>en</ex></expan> waltman <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> dıener <expan>empote<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l6">von Mertein Geuders vnd Matheis wenigheıncʒen <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l7"><expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> wegen / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<del rend="strikethrough"> gne </del> <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> brief vnd auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l8">des <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> dieners gewerbe von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden dorauff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l9">wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> / vnd beſunder daʒ <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade wıſſen wölle / </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l10">ob der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> <expan>Math<ex>eis</ex></expan> wenigheincʒ ein eekind ſeẏ oder niht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l11">Alſo laſſen wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnaden wiſſen daʒ etlıch erber 
<del rend="strikethrough">leute </del> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l12">frum leute <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> von <expan>deſſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>vvenigheincʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l13">Burgers wegen vor vns geweſen ſein / Vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l14">geſagt bey iren eyden / daʒ der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan> <expan>Math<ex>eis</ex></expan> <expan>Wenıgh<ex>eincʒ</ex></expan> in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l15">Stat hıe geporen vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">ein </del> von vater vnd Muter ein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l18">rechts eekinde ſeẏ / darümb ſo <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_11_line_1570542573273_25">vvir </ab></add> aber 
<del rend="strikethrough">von der <expan>egeſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan></del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l19">
<del rend="strikethrough">ſache w </del> cʒu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>Mark<ex>art</ex></expan> waltman <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l20">dıener von <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>bit<ex>en</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l22">vvaʒ <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> / <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> cʒu diſem 
<del rend="strikethrough"> male </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_11_r1l21">male </ab></add> an ewr gnade </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l23">werb von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_11_line_1570543357937_57">daʒ </ab></add> Jm des <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_11_r1l24">Jn <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>gnedıkl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> von ew <expan>vertıge<ex>n</ex></expan> wollet Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_11" id="4r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Bysschoff czu <expan>Bamb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> oder wer
                                <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan> gewalt hat in geistlichen sachen
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, als wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden
                        vormals <expan>geschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und bey dem
                                <expan>Markart<ex>en</ex></expan> Waltman,
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> diener, <expan>empote<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von Mertein Geuders und Matheis Wenigheinczen,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, wegen, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> brief und auch des
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
                        dieners, gewerbe von <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden dorauff wol
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> und besunder, daz
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade wissen wölle, ob der
                                <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>Math<ex>eis</ex></expan> Wenigheincz ein eekind sey oder niht; also
                        lassen wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnaden wissen, daz etlich erber und
                        frum leute, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, von <expan>desselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Wenigheincze<ex>n</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
                        burgers, wegen vor uns gewesen sein und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                        gesagt bey iren eyden, daz der <expan>egen<ex>ante</ex></expan>
<expan>Math<ex>eis</ex></expan>
<expan>Wenigh<ex>eincz</ex></expan> in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat
                        hie geporen und von vater und muter ein rechts eekinde sey. Darümb so
                                <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan>
<add>wir</add> aber czu <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnade<ex>n</ex></expan> den <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Mark<ex>art</ex></expan> Waltman, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
                        diener, von <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache
                            <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> czu <expan>rede<ex>n</ex></expan> und
                                <expan>bit<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., waz
                            <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> czu disem
                            <add>male</add> an ewr gnade werb von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, <add>daz</add> im des
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnade <expan>gelaub<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und
                        in <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedikl<ex>ichen</ex></expan> von ew <expan>vertige<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wollet, als etc. Das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
